S

S_Record - Class in <Unnamed>
This class handles loading and saving of Motorola S-Record files which take the following format

+-------------------//------------------//-----------------------+
| Type | Count | Address | ----- Data ---- | Checksum |
+-------------------//------------------//-----------------------+

The Type field contains two characters which describe the type of record, i.e.

Default constructor takes the memory array as a parameter
